{"tid":1015810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[機師VS地勤]忍不住了！反對機師罷工 地勤號召200員工交通部抗議","createTime":"2019-02-10T10:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T13:51:33.000Z","uid":141026,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"448904dee753cf16fdd6ec3c61d91d49ea8e316b","tid":1015810,"uid":141026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:33:47.000Z","msg":"華航機師罷工來到第3天，目前已造成取消超過50個航班，適逢農曆春節假期，許多遊客的行程被打亂，而站在第一線面對遊客抱怨的地勤，現在也決定和內部員工串聯，號召約200人，預計今天（10號）下午3點30分在東門市場前集合，再前往交通部抗議。<br />\n<br />\n桃園市機師職業工會主動旗下華航分會自2月8日起發動無預警罷工，造成華航非機師同仁利益受損，亦泯滅社會大眾新年期間空中交通權益，基此，華航其他同仁擬向交通部陳情，希能為中華航空公司絕大多數同仁，「依法」保障既有權益。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n一、 請交通部拒絕接受機師工會訴求，維持目前航空器飛航作業管理規則（AOR）進行組員派遣。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n二、 現行溝通協調會議，拒絕本公司高階主管面談，卻容忍非華航之機師工會代表進入談判，顯違反公平正義原則，亦不具華航同仁代表性。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n三、 桃園市機師工會華航成員僅占華航約一成之員工，交通部談判結果欠缺結論比例原則。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n基於上述原則，擬請交通部以及勞動部宣告本次罷工違法，回歸工會法罷工相關程序，回應本公司提出調解以及仲裁之訴求。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n時間、地點如下：<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n一、時間：15:30<br />\n二、集合地點：東門市場捷運站<br />\n三、服裝：白色上衣（儘量）<br />\n四、口號：華航員工、反對罷工。停止罷工、回來開工。綁架旅客、人神共憤。交通部會，出來面對。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ebc.net.tw/News/Article/151799\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ebc.net.tw%2FNews%2FArticle%2F151799&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=2b0ee09d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ebc.net.tw/News/Article/151799</a>"},{"pid":"5006b73c8cc3d4cc30dc96b8309a5be62c4bf373","tid":1015810,"uid":141026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 快訊／「反對機師罷工」　上百華航地勤集結穿白衣16時交通部抗議 | ETtoday生活 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190210/1374866.htm#ixzz5f7hexT5E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190210%2F1374866.htm%23ixzz5f7hexT5E&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=d28e0797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190210/1374866.htm#ixzz5f7hexT5E</a> <br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"2a5167c7814f0ad44c06caa33fa854c28a1d0c16","tid":1015810,"uid":51932,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:35:49.000Z","msg":"屌，小農DNA <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2913e608885f0fa467c17eced67e44f953aff7","tid":1015810,"uid":43041,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:36:00.000Z","msg":"擺明公司搞"},{"pid":"818071da326f0476d40d435b1ba8c966aa050b76","tid":1015810,"uid":41818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:36:57.000Z","msg":"佢地個地勤工會好似分開 依家無份又要幫手執屎"},{"pid":"74d6bd3a1ea2bafccc9bbfab6a699e6f2c1516cb","tid":1015810,"uid":56698,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"818071da326f0476d40d435b1ba8c966aa050b76","tid":1015810,"uid":41818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:36:57.000Z","msg":"佢地個地勤工會好似分開 依家無份又要幫手執屎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:38:47.000Z","msg":"一齊罷工精彩啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922c8855dc3da96e2767eaf5ef266af6fa3c32ff","tid":1015810,"uid":2054,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fDaFWV9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfDaFWV9.png&h=6c009d34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b6ceab7fe13a16148a4c94a7406aadd07e1212b","tid":1015810,"uid":174420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:41:52.000Z","msg":"罷工又要搞到其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14da2538152df192ea03201ca39a5f3a032db2fe","tid":1015810,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201